多貨輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d871d88a055d099ee315e31a35544320ddef15","tid":305740,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"航空母艦無其他船跟住做戰鬥群，捱唔捱到3分鐘？"},{"pid":"dd500f41b32942bca9887d3ea013adf3feee0e24","tid":305740,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除左香港架野去得邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇核動力..去到台灣已經冇油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今年1年已經試過圍台灣一圈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/index.php/news/politics/breakingnews/1944840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F1944840&d=e3ajFMWzfO%2FATASwrcDSbMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3f2f8fac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F1944840&h=9c56a758\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/index.php/news/politics/breakingnews/1944840</a>"},{"pid":"1867e24481a6ccab8262d03c4454ef1bcf9b8526","tid":305740,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>航空母艦無其他船跟住做戰鬥群，捱唔捱到3分鐘？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似可以秒速變做潛艇"},{"pid":"61bb1ba0d9ed231784f895cc36e1f49dfdfea097","tid":305740,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎㗎幾十年前，龍骨都唔知幾成新嘅船就想人愛國，唔係咁少家掛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一件軍備, 可唔可以令人愛國, 同先唔先進無關係<br />\n主要係睇你既作為<br />\n<br />\n如果你拎架幾十年前既軍備, 去保護國家, 保護市民, 一樣可以令人愛國<br />\n如果你拎架最先進既軍備, 去殺自己人民, 一樣會令人反感<br />\n<br />\n而中共就是拎軍備去殺自己人民<br />\n所以不論中共軍備幾先進, 都會令人反感"}]}